{"type":"message","id":"c1dcc433","parentId":"dfafaabb","timestamp":"2026-03-26T07:21:49.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"24的版本你更新了什么\"。这个问题比较模糊，可能是指：\n1. 某个软件的第24个版本\n2. 2024年的版本\n3. 24号这一天的更新\n4. 其他与\"24\"相关的版本\n\n从上下文看，这是飞书私信，但 sender 信息只显示了 open_id，没有显示名字。这个 open_id `ou_687cb7ea47f1d583ccc63627705571d4` 与 USER.md 中记录的小王子的 open_id `ou_45ca8d7feaddef8a7a182779a434c8bc` 不同，所以这不是小王子。\n\n根据 AGENTS.md 的指示，我应该先读取：\n1. SOUL.md - 已在上下文中\n2. USER.md - 已在上下文中  \n3. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (今天 + 昨天)\n\n今天是 2026-03-26，我应该检查 memory/2026-03-26.md 和 memory/2026-03-25.md 看看有没有关于\"24版本\"的记录。\n\n同时，由于这不是小王子（open_id 不匹配），根据 AGENTS.md 的规则，在非 MAIN SESSION（与人类的直接对话）中，我不应该加载 MEMORY.md。\n\n让我先读取记忆文件看看有没有相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我查查最近的记忆记录，看看有没有关于\"24版本\"的信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a538bb1f5534f59a507e524","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar/memory/2026-03-26.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_37b8bbb938de4f72ad23fded","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar/memory/2026-03-25.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ec16b89fbfbc43fba351e79f","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-avatar/memory/2026-03-24.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":11831,"output":670,"cacheRead":1472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13973,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774509694415,"responseId":"2026032615213475a5f0a6ccd548d0"}}
