{"type":"message","id":"86bab03c","parentId":"e3f23c74","timestamp":"2026-03-26T09:06:47.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前安装的是 4.1.0.13，但 apt 源里没有更新的版本候选（候选版本和已安装版本一样）。这说明微信可能是通过手动下载 deb 包安装的，没有配置自动更新的 apt 源。\n\n让我查一下最新版本的微信 Linux 版本是多少。从微信官网下载页面获取。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bf7c464da7f14b6ab9a2e2fb","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"微信 Linux 版本下载 最新版本 2025","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":398,"output":163,"cacheRead":30976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31537,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774515984602,"responseId":"20260326170624339219e238d64420"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c22c629e","parentId":"86bab03c","timestamp":"2026-03-26T09:06:54.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bf7c464da7f14b6ab9a2e2fb","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"微信 Linux 版本下载 最新版本 2025\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 6107,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b1ca86fb2cd9ce4c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWeixin for Linux\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b1ca86fb2cd9ce4c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://linux.weixin.qq.com/en\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a717d70d2c54f4ae\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nA cross-platform communication tool. Supports one-to-one and multi-person chat. Send voice, picture, video, and text messages through mobile networks.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a717d70d2c54f4ae\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"linux.weixin.qq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e5e23a47df373e3f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n微信，是一个生活方式\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e5e23a47df373e3f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://weixin.qq.com/updates?amp=&platform=linux&version=4.1.0\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85480afd3890f2fe\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n发布日期： 2025-10-31 · 发布版本： 微信 <strong>4.1.0 for Linux</strong> 下载最新版本\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"85480afd3890f2fe\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"weixin.qq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e07fea6eca66972c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n【Ubuntu】在Ubuntu上安装微信 - 清风来叙 - 博客园\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e07fea6eca66972c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cn