{"type":"message","id":"b5e1ae45","parentId":"c22c629e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T09:07:14.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从搜索结果看，微信 Linux 最新版本是 4.1.0，而用户当前安装的就是 4.1.0.13。看起来已经是最新版本了。\n\n但用户说\"提示微信版本太低了\"，这可能是：\n1. 微信客户端内部的版本检查提示（可能是服务器端的最低版本要求变了）\n2. 或者用户看到的是某个特定功能需要更高版本\n\n让我直接访问微信 Linux 官网看看最新版本号。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd88a9f5b48e4a82a25472ba","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://linux.weixin.qq.com/","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1365,"output":214,"cacheRead":31360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32939,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774516014100,"responseId":"202603261706543f5fa92189a04750"}}
