{"type":"message","id":"adec4028","parentId":"b75dc973","timestamp":"2026-03-26T11:54:15.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户描述了几个电商相关的需求：\n\n1. 对接企业微信或个人微信做客服，喂数据自动回复\n2. 自动抓取抖音数据，特别是同行卖家的数据\n3. 自动化工作流，批量抓取同行爆款图片到本地文件夹（淘宝、抖音、小红书）\n\n这些需求需要不同的技能。让我分析一下需要什么技能：\n\n1. **微信客服自动回复** - 需要对接企业微信或个人微信的技能\n   - 已经有 feishu 相关的技能，但用户要的是微信\n   - 可能需要查看有没有微信相关的技能\n\n2. **抓取抖音数据** - 需要爬虫/数据抓取技能\n   - 可能需要 browser 自动化或爬虫相关的技能\n\n3. **批量抓取图片** - 需要图片抓取技能\n   - 可能需要 browser 自动化技能来抓取图片\n\n让我搜索一下相关的技能。\n","thinkingSignature":"38cf907f0028cec294ff86cb4665f68e2eb094cba34bc5f533aea0d40d9904af"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfm3crv9snt2_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills search wechat"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfm3crv9snt2_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills search douyin"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfm3crv9snt2_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills search browser"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rfm3crv9snt2_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills search scrap"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64041,"output":282,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64515,"cost":{"input":0.019212299999999998,"output":0.0003384,"cacheRead":0.000005759999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019556459999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526039325,"responseId":"06145157bf4b069c0f022cab4b88f9d9"}}
