{"type":"message","id":"24b07274","parentId":"4c565185","timestamp":"2026-03-26T11:54:55.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了很多技能搜索结果。让我整理一下用户需求对应的技能：\n\n用户需求：\n1. 对接企业微信或个人微信做客服，喂数据自动回复\n2. 自动抓取抖音数据，特别是同行卖家数据\n3. 自动化工作流，批量抓取同行爆款图片到本地（淘宝、抖音、小红书）\n\n对应的技能：\n\n**微信相关：**\n- wechat - WeChat Connect（连接微信）\n- wechat-auto-reply - 半自动回复\n- wechat-automation - 自动化（macOS）\n\n**抖音相关：**\n- douyin-hot-trend - 抖音热榜\n- douyin-downloader - 抖音视频下载\n- douyin-video-analyst - 抖音账号视频批量采集与文案分析\n- douyin-dl - 抖音视频下载\n\n**浏览器自动化/抓取：**\n- browser-automation / agent-browser - 浏览器自动化（用于抓取图片）\n- scrape-web / scrapling-web-scraper - 网页抓取\n\n让我安装这些技能。对于微信，需要看看是否需要特殊配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"ca60ceed15ad9bbbeb923c74abc0ee7bc7bfcda890788aec27da2e10ecb0ae98"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，我来帮你安装这些电商相关的技能。根据你的需求，我整理了以下技能：\n\n**微信客服/自动回复：**\n- `wechat` - 连接微信\n- `wechat-automation` - 微信自动化（macOS）\n\n**抖音数据抓取：**\n- `douyin-hot-trend` - 抖音热榜\n- `douyin-video-analyst` - 抖音视频批量采集分析\n- `douyin-downloader` - 抖音视频下载\n\n**图片批量抓取（淘宝、抖音、小红书）：**\n- `agent-browser` - 浏览器自动化\n- `scrapling-web-scraper` - 隐身网页抓取\n\n让我开始安装：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fmtaglk3zisw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills install wechat-automation","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1812,"output":407,"cacheRead":65152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67371,"cost":{"input":0.0005436,"output":0.0004883999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0019545599999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029865599999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526079126,"responseId":"0614517f6d0f2133478576fec44fa3c8"}}
